                                    <p class="right-pera">The fear window is a period that is said to be most evident
                                        between 8 to around 11 weeks, when your puppy may seem to be afraid of
                                        everything. It’s important during this period that they ideally don’t experience
                                        any traumatic events, as these could leave a life long imprint on your dog.
                                        Given that this
                                        period usually coincides with bringing your puppy into your home, it’s good to
                                        have a plan for introducing your puppy to your human kids.</p>
                                    <p>
                                    <ol start="1">
