                                            she iscomfortable with it. No squeezing or squealing with excitement.</li>
                                        <li>Never allow children to poke or chase a puppy, and always allow them to rest
                                            and sleepwhen they need it.</li>
                                        <li>Puppies should never be left alone with young children.</li>
