                                <span class="vicki-tip">Vicki’s Tip</span>
                                <p>When puppy is attempting to ask you to play by biting you or your clothing; ask them
                                    to find their “tug-tug”. Puppy will learn that the most successful means of engaging
                                    you in a game is to offer the toy.</p>
